r +15 vsMg +5 vsFire +5 vsCold +25 Mana<br>-Face: Gangrenous Beetle Mask, +7 AC +5 Str +5 Dex +10 vsDis +20 Mana <br>-Ear1: Cougar Claw, +4 AC +3 Str +2 Dex<br>-Ear2: Vah Shir Claw, +5 AC, +6 DEX, +4 STA<br>-Shoulders: Guardian Pauldrons, +14 AC +4 Str +2 Dex +6 vsMg +10 HP<br>-Chest: Guardian BP, +22 AC +7 Str +7 Sta +5 vsMg +5 vsFire<br>-Arms: Guardian Arms, +12 AC +5 Str +4 Dex +15 HP +15 Mana <br>-Bracer1: Deepwater Bracer, +16 AC effect: stun<br>-Bracer2: Guardian Bracer, +9 AC +3 Sta +3 Dex +4 vsMg +5 vsFire +5 vsCold +10 HP +10 Mana<br>-Hands: Silver Chitin Hand Wraps, +5 AC +3 vsMg +3 vsFire +3 vsCold +3 vsPos +3 vsDis HASTE<br>-Finger1: Jagged band, ac5 str3<br>-Finger2: Jagged band, ac5 str3<br>-Back: Spider Fur Cloak, +10 AC +4 Str +4 Sta +6 vsCold<br>-Waist: Axgoreth Belt of Defense, +20 AC +15 Str +15 Wis <br>-Legs: Guardian Leggings, +12 AC +4 Str +4 Wis +5 Cha +5 vsMg +15 vsFire +15 vsCold +15 HP <br>-Feet: Shrouded Boots, +12 AC +4 Str +4 Sta +4 Agi +4 Dex +4 Wis +4 Int +5 Cha<br>-Range: Gordan's Idol, +15 AC +12 Str +10 Agi +5 vsCold +5 vsPos +25 HP<br><br>- 2 Hand Slash: Strength of Grodan, 41 dmg 51 del +25 Str +10 Sta<br>-1 Hand Slash: Sword of the Morning, 16 dmg 27 del +10 Dex Effect: Tishans Clash<br>-Shield: Shield of Stalwart Seas, +35 AC +20 Str +20 Sta<br><br>Valdesero 54 lvl Pally on Cazic-Thule Server <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udpawson.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dpawson</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 94<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/15/02 9:55:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=211.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.pattyanddave.com/dave/lr/pics/ZsaFace.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Please Help me Spend Some Money : )</span><hr size=1> Things I would do...<br><br>Replace the Cougar Claw with a Wolf Fang. If you sell the Cougar Claw, this may cost you nothing, and stamina is more useful than dexterity.<br><br>Replace the rings with AC6 HP65 rings. Doing both fingers should cost you well under 1000pp. If you are ambitious, you could instead try to hunt for a Shadel Bandit Ring for one finger.<br><br>Get some Deepwater Boots. That's just a lot of AC to give up. On Drinal you'd get those for under 1000, most likely.<br><br>The last obvious thing I might do is to replace your bp with Barbed Ringmail. On Drinal that would run you about 4k or so these days if you were patient. It all depends what you think your prospects are for getting a drop. If you do Fear, Thurg, whatever often, and thing you might see a drop, stick it out. If not, it will be a nice upgrade.<br><br>There are plenty of other things you could do, but these jump out at me, and even if you did everything I suggest, you'd still have plenty of cash left over.<br><br>Hope this helps...<br> <p><TABLE BORDER=0><TR><TD>Dave, speaking for ZsaZsa</TD></TR><TR><TD>ZsaZsa Vavoom of Drinal</TD></TR><TR><TD>55th Level Paladin, Inmate of the Arcane Asylum, and Keeper of the Funk</TD></TR><TR><TD><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=20375"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="http://www.pattyanddave.com/dave/aa/pic/DWSig.jpg"></A></TD></TR></TABLE></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uangelsyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Angelsyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 175<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/15/02 9:51:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=211.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Please Help me Spend Some Money : )</span><hr size=1> ZsaZsa got here first, but I agree... your BP &amp; Boots are your weakest points.<br><br>Go on Planar raids, Kael Raids, whatever it takes to get Valorium/Runed Protector/Velious Quest gear.<br><br>You're walking around in some of the kind of armour that my Paladin wears at 43!  Even Royal Frosted Velium would be an upgrade for many of your pieces. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=211.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=211.topic&index=2><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.emailToFriend?topicID=211.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.threadControl?topicID=211.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=211.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email no